# =============================================================================
# Blue Mountains National Park ONLY
# =============================================================================
# Deploy ONLY into this domain's document root, e.g.:
#   public_html/bluemountainsnationalpark/
#
# Do NOT upload this file to:
#   public_html/                    (farmingdomains.com root)
#   public_html/domains/            (Farming Domains portfolio pages)
#   any other site's folder
#
# cPanel addon domains with their own docroot only apply rules from THEIR
# folder. This file cannot affect farmingdomains.com if it stays in BM's root.
# =============================================================================

DirectoryIndex index.html

# Astro static 404 (file must exist in this same docroot as 404.html)
ErrorDocument 404 /404.html

# Do NOT add: Redirect /blog → /domains  (domains/ belongs to farmingdomains.com)
